  <entry>
    <title>Tarjan求强连通分量</title>
    <link href="https://gzezfisher.top/2019/11/21/2019-11-21-%E5%BC%BA%E8%BF%9E%E9%80%9A%E5%88%86%E9%87%8F/"/>
    <id>https://gzezfisher.top/2019/11/21/2019-11-21-%E5%BC%BA%E8%BF%9E%E9%80%9A%E5%88%86%E9%87%8F/</id>
    <published>2019-11-21T09:32:59.000Z</published>
    <updated>2021-04-26T10:52:26.950Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="强连通分量是什么"><a href="#强连通分量是什么" class="headerlink" title="强连通分量是什么"></a>强连通分量是什么</h1><h2 id="前置知识"><a href="#前置知识" class="headerlink" title="前置知识"></a>前置知识</h2><p><strong>dfs生成树</strong>：</p><p><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20181107145629233.png"></p><p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2019/11/23/YXJ4ruCDgREwBT2.png" alt="image"></p><p>设 $dfn[i]$ 为访问 $i$ 节点 的 dfs 序,bool 变量 $vis[i]$ 表示 $i$ 节点是否被访问过了.现有一条有向边 $( u, v )$.</p><p><strong>若 $dfn[v] &gt; dfn[u]$,则边 $( u, v )$ 为树枝边或前向边</strong><br>若 $vis[v] == false$,则该边为树枝边<br>若 $vis[v] == true$,则该边为前向边<br><strong>若 $dfn[v] &lt; dfn[u]$,则边 $( u, v )$ 为后向边或横叉边</strong><br>若点 $v$ 是点 $u$ 的祖先,则该边为后向边<br>若点 $v$ 不是点 $u$ 的祖先,则该边为横叉边<br><img src="https://i.loli.net/2019/12/30/XNPhGKlUSw1FO5d.png" alt="638419-20151128184040687-313147708.png"></p><span id="more"></span><p><strong>强连通</strong>:</p><blockquote><p>如果两个顶点$i,j$间$(i&gt;j)$有一条从$i$到$j$的有向路径,同时还有一条从$j$到$i$的有向路径,则称两个顶点强连通</p></blockquote><p><strong>强连通图</strong>：</p><blockquote><p>如果有向图$G$的每两个顶点都强连通,称$G$是一个强连通图</p></blockquote><h2 id="强连通分量"><a href="#强连通分量" class="headerlink" title="强连通分量"></a>强连通分量</h2><blockquote><p>有向图的极大强连通子图,称为强连通分量</p></blockquote><p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2019/11/23/PAYJxQyLW3pzOMX.png" alt="image"></p><p>图中点$1,2,3,4$是一个强连通分量.</p><h1 id="Tarjan求强连通分量"><a href="#Tarjan求强连通分量" class="headerlink" title="Tarjan求强连通分量"></a>Tarjan求强连通分量</h1><p>Tarjan算法是基于对图深度优先搜索的算法,每个强连通分量为搜索树中的一棵子树.搜索时,把当前搜索树中未处理的节点加入一个堆栈,回溯时可以判断栈顶到栈中的节点是否为一个强连通分量.</p><p>定义$dfn[u]$为节点$u$搜索的次序编号(时间戳),$low[u]$为$u$或$u$的子树能够追溯到的最早的栈中节点的次序号.</p><p>$low[u]=min(dfn[u],low[v] (树枝边),dfn[v] (强连通分量内的后向边和横插边))$</p><p>当$dfn[u]=low[u]$时,以$u$为根的搜索子树上所有节点(即栈中的点)是一个强连通分量.</p><h1 id="代码实现"><a href="#代码实现" class="headerlink" title="代码实现"></a>代码实现</h1><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">tarjan</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> k)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    num++;</span><br><span class="line">    dfn[k]=low[k]=num;</span><br><span class="line">    st.<span class="built_in">push</span>(k);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="keyword">int</span> i=<span class="number">0</span>; i&lt;g[k].<span class="built_in">size</span>() ; i++) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">int</span> t=g[k][i];</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span>(dfn[t]==<span class="number">0</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="built_in">tarjan</span>(t);</span><br><span class="line">            low[k]=<span class="built_in">min</span>(low[k],low[t]);</span><br><span class="line">        &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span>(!color[t]) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                low[k]=<span class="built_in">min</span>(low[k],dfn[t]);</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(dfn[k]==low[k]) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        col++;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">int</span> s;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">do</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            s=st.<span class="built_in">top</span>();</span><br><span class="line">            st.<span class="built_in">pop</span>();</span><br><span class="line">            color[s]=col;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125; <span class="keyword">while</span>(s!=k);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;h1 id=&quot;强连通分量是什么&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#强连通分量是什么&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;强连通分量是什么&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;强连通分量是什么&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;h2 id=&quot;前置知识&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#前置知识&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;前置知识&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;前置知识&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;dfs生成树&lt;/strong&gt;：&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20181107145629233.png&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://i.loli.net/2019/11/23/YXJ4ruCDgREwBT2.png&quot; alt=&quot;image&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;设 $dfn[i]$ 为访问 $i$ 节点 的 dfs 序,bool 变量 $vis[i]$ 表示 $i$ 节点是否被访问过了.现有一条有向边 $( u, v )$.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;若 $dfn[v] &amp;gt; dfn[u]$,则边 $( u, v )$ 为树枝边或前向边&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;若 $vis[v] == false$,则该边为树枝边&lt;br&gt;若 $vis[v] == true$,则该边为前向边&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;若 $dfn[v] &amp;lt; dfn[u]$,则边 $( u, v )$ 为后向边或横叉边&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;若点 $v$ 是点 $u$ 的祖先,则该边为后向边&lt;br&gt;若点 $v$ 不是点 $u$ 的祖先,则该边为横叉边&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://i.loli.net/2019/12/30/XNPhGKlUSw1FO5d.png&quot; alt=&quot;638419-20151128184040687-313147708.png&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</summary>
    
    
    
