    <category term="Tarjan" scheme="https://gzezfisher.top/tags/Tarjan/"/>
    
  </entry>
  
  <entry>
    <title>二叉堆的实现</title>
    <link href="https://gzezfisher.top/2019/11/10/2019-11-10-%E4%BA%8C%E5%8F%89%E5%A0%86%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0/"/>
    <id>https://gzezfisher.top/2019/11/10/2019-11-10-%E4%BA%8C%E5%8F%89%E5%A0%86%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0/</id>
    <published>2019-11-10T08:18:18.000Z</published>
    <updated>2021-04-26T10:52:22.322Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="二叉堆是什么"><a href="#二叉堆是什么" class="headerlink" title="二叉堆是什么"></a>二叉堆是什么</h1><blockquote><p>二叉堆是一种特殊的堆,二叉堆是完全二叉树.二叉堆有两种：大根堆和小根堆.大根堆：父结点的键值总是大于或等于任何一个子节点的键值；小根堆：父结点的键值总是小于或等于任何一个子节点的键值.</p></blockquote><span id="more"></span><p>二叉堆是一棵树,所以能用一维数组实现.</p><p><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20181218114932533" alt="二叉堆"></p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title">p_queue</span>&#123;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> node[<span class="number">10000005</span>],len<span class="comment">/*标记长度*/</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">p_queue</span>()&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">memset</span>(node,<span class="number">0</span>,<span class="built_in"><span class="keyword">sizeof</span></span>(node));</span><br><span class="line">len=<span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">/*未完*/</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="基本操作"><a href="#基本操作" class="headerlink" title="基本操作"></a>基本操作</h1><p>首先是<strong>push</strong>操作。<br>二叉堆的插入方法是先将要插入的数存在堆的最后,再从下往上遍历.如果这个节点比父亲节点小,则交换两个节点,否则停止遍历.</p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">push</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> x)</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">len++;</span><br><span class="line">node[len]=x;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> s=len;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">while</span>(node[s]&lt;node[s/<span class="number">2</span>])&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">swap</span>(node[s],node[s/<span class="number">2</span>]);</span><br><span class="line">s/=<span class="number">2</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>其次是<strong>pop</strong>操作.删除操作是把根节点换成最后的节点,在从上往下遍历.<br>如果这个节点比较小的子节点小,则交换两个节点,否则停止遍历.</p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">pop</span><span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">node[<span class="number">1</span>]=node[len];</span><br><span class="line">node[len]=<span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">len--;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> s=<span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">while</span>(node[s]&gt;<span class="built_in">min</span>(node[s*<span class="number">2</span>],node[s*<span class="number">2</span>+<span class="number">1</span>])&amp;&amp;s*<span class="number">2</span>&lt;=len)&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span>(node[s*<span class="number">2</span>]&lt;node[s*<span class="number">2</span>+<span class="number">1</span>]||s*<span class="number">2</span>+<span class="number">1</span>&gt;len)&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">swap</span>(node[s],node[s*<span class="number">2</span>]);</span><br><span class="line">s=s*<span class="number">2</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">swap</span>(node[s],node[s*<span class="number">2</span>+<span class="number">1</span>]);</span><br><span class="line">s=s*<span class="number">2</span>+<span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>最后是一些简单的操作</p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">top</span><span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">return</span> node[<span class="number">1</span>];</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">size</span><span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">return</span> len;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">bool</span> <span class="title">empty</span><span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">return</span> len^<span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="STL中的二叉堆"><a href="#STL中的二叉堆" class="headerlink" title="STL中的二叉堆"></a>STL中的二叉堆</h1><p><code>priority_queue &lt;int&gt; q</code></p><p>push操作:<code>q.push(a)</code></p><p>pop操作:<code>q.pop()</code></p><p>其它:</p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">q.<span class="built_in">top</span>();</span><br><span class="line">q.<span class="built_in">size</span>();</span><br><span class="line">q.<span class="built_in">empty</span>();</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;h1 id=&quot;二叉堆是什么&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#二叉堆是什么&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;二叉堆是什么&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;二叉堆是什么&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;二叉堆是一种特殊的堆,二叉堆是完全二叉树.二叉堆有两种：大根堆和小根堆.大根堆：父结点的键值总是大于或等于任何一个子节点的键值；小根堆：父结点的键值总是小于或等于任何一个子节点的键值.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;</summary>
    
    
    
